snippet.title: Firewall Ultra Developer Presentation Trailer - Future Games Show Summer Showcase 2023
snippet.description:
https://www.youtube.com/@FutureGamesShow

Firewall Ultra is a tactical shooter coming exclusively to PS VR 2 later this year, and First Contact Entertainment delivered a developer presentation for the game during this year's Summer Showcase.

#FutureGamesShow #FGS
